    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you use a warlord feature as a Bonus Action and are wielding a weapon in each hand, you may make a single weapon attack as part of the same Bonus Action dealing bonus damage equal to your Charisma modifier (minimum of 1). An Icon of Victory is able to use their Shield in place of a weapon for the purpose of this Command Style.</p><p>Additionally, allies that hit as a result of your Strike like Iron or Spotter's Order can replace their weapon's mastery property for this attack with one of your mastery properties.</p>",
